"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Great news for the **Rigel Protocol** community! Our Dev team is now finishing the integration with the **Polygon Matic** network.\\n\\nPolygon combines the best of **Ethereum** and sovereign blockchains into a full-fledged multi-chain system. It solves pain points associated with Blockchains, like high gas fees and slow speeds, without sacrificing on security and combining the best of Ethereum and sovereign blockchains into an attractive feature set.\\n\\n5 million RGP on Ethereum will be burned and minted on the **Polygon Matic** network on 08/01/2022.\\n\\nCountdown to the Burning Event: <https://www.tickcounter.com/countdown/2953456/rgp-burn>\\n\\n## The RGP tokenomics on Polygon will be as follows:\\n\\n* **Maximum Supply**: 5 Million RGP\\n* **Margin Liquidity Rewards:** 2 Million RGP\\n* **Yield Farming** : 1.5 Million RGP\\n* **Referrals:** 200,000 RGP\\n* **Reserves:** 1,300,000 RGP\\n\\nThe **Polygon Network** functionalities will be incorporated to the Rigel Protocol ecosystem applications like SmartSwap and the GiftDapp, and the subsequent integrations with other applications and features in development like the margin Exchange and Smart Bid.\\n\\nWith Polygon, any project can easily spin-up a dedicated blockchain network which combines the best features of stand-alone blockchains (sovereignty, scalability and flexibility) and Ethereum (security, interoperability and developer experience). Additionally, these blockchains are compatible with all the existing Ethereum tools (Metamask, MyCrypto, Remix etc), and can exchange messages among themselves and with Ethereum.\\n\\nWell, we saved the best for last. Our very own native token (RGP) would be coming live on the polygon network to facilitate all our Dapps. **All RGPs Holders and Stakers (RGP Liquidity Providers) on both Ethereum and Binance Smart chain would receive 1/10 of their held amount(*this means for 10 RGPs you hold you receive 1 on the polygon network via the same address*). So stack Up** RGPs.\\n\\nThe **RGP Snapshot,** to record the addresses holding or staking RGP at that time**,** will take place on 10/01/2022.\\n\\nCountdown for the Snapshot: <https://www.tickcounter.com/countdown/2953464/rgp-snapshot>\\n\\nThe RGP drop will be distributed within 2 weeks from the Snapshot.\\n\\n## What to expect?\\n\\n* Polygon RGPs distribution to BSC/ETH holders (stakers)\\n* Polygon Network integration to our GiftDapp & Smartswap\\n* New Farms on the Polygon network\\n* Launchpad\\n\\n**Get on board now! More amazing events and partnerships are on the way!**\",\"timestamp\":1640308113,\"title\":\"Rigel Protocol is coming to Polygon! Free Airdrop for RGP Hodlers!\"},\"digest\":\"xe-VCqR2dtld_Lp82qYKWlpH5DpGzEtyexkYeNQ8q_4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x78A60DBDbb8f80837fc910fC8f0BB2235Ec2b6aA\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"MXT855ulGG60jk6WHddQQt70LD6R0GutH4xinjVvxqc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"7pCWRWQTLmTMzUHKlaQDUjEXUfQVhBa54JVdIcF0hEA\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"ZR9Z_hzelAeTptn1r29nnZ-CsjqM4tFA3_4Aczaj215KGhBivLuch1TJVb2TIYpdWU5tuafrFrJSJKdgyBbS1A\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x710b5adeb10c705b3510af31f4529f786096a59e641a077e05e36d8cf8e24f1e29414cdb527c608099cad8f94249bc0a2159d66c357a1a4bed703c79cce510b91c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"MXT855ulGG60jk6WHddQQt70LD6R0GutH4xinjVvxqc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"7pCWRWQTLmTMzUHKlaQDUjEXUfQVhBa54JVdIcF0hEA\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"xe-VCqR2dtld_Lp82qYKWlpH5DpGzEtyexkYeNQ8q_4\"}"